2.5 Memory Service
2.5.1 Authoritative Responsibilities & Operational Scope
* Tiered Tenancy Isolation: Enforces strict logical and cryptographic separation across four memory tiers:
   1. Private Tier (MEMORY_TIER_PRIVATE): Accessible exclusively by the individual human Gaia ID and their Personal Agent.
   2. Workstream Tier (MEMORY_TIER_WORKSTREAM): Shared across all teammates and agent runtimes bound to a specific workstream.
   3. Team / Organization Tier (MEMORY_TIER_TEAM): Cross-workstream organizational knowledge, shared architectural patterns, and verified debugging recipes.
   4. Global Tier (MEMORY_TIER_GLOBAL): System-wide immutable Google3 engineering conventions, style guides, and baseline facts.
